description	"Mandalore the Preserver

Class: Clone Trooper.
Class Summary: 
A tanky commander with a heavy repeater, quickthrow grenades and a long-reaching vibro-sword. 

Weaponry:
- Repeating Blaster (Based on Clone Rifle 2)
- Ion Blobs (3)
- Frag Grenades (3)
- Vibro-Sword *
- Heavy Melee

* Special Weapon Descriptions:
--- Vibro-Sword
- Defense (1)
- Can use Yellow and Red styles
- Melee weapon based on Lightsaber
- Deals reduced damage
- Cannot block blaster fire
- Can block lightsabers

Attributes:
- Rally
- Cortosis
- Magnetic Plating
- Blast Armor
- Recharging Shields (1)

Abilities:
- Stamina (3) [Class Special 1]
- Quick Throw (1) [Alt Ability 1]
--- Grappling Hook (2)
- Hold Class Special 2 while melee is equipped, then hold spacebar to ascend or crouch to descend.

Canderous Ordo, later known as Mandalore the Preserver, was a Mandalorian of Clan Ordo who fought in the Mandalorian Wars and earned significant glory and prestige with his bold tactics and leadership."